OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FRoyals and faith leaders will gather
OL,8,Ffor a moment of history when the first
OL,9,Fwoman to take the role of top bishop
OL,10,Fin the Church of England is enthroned.
OL,12,FA service before around 2,000 people
OL,13,Fon Wednesday will mark the symbolic
OL,14,Fstart to Dame Sarah Mullally's
OL,15,Fministry as Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
