PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales are
OL,8,Fset to join those gathered in
OL,9,FCanterbury Cathedral to see the 106th
OL,10,FArchbishop of Canterbury ` and first
OL,11,Ffemale to hold the high office in its
OL,12,F1,400-year history ` officially
OL,13,Finstalled.
OL,15,FThe ceremony will celebrate women,
OL,16,FDame Sarah has said, as she outlined
OL,17,Fhow her historic appointment shows
OL,18,F"it's entirely possible for you to
OL,19,Ffollow your dreams and what you want
OL,20,Fto do".
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
