CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FWhile the King is technically head of
OL,8,Fthe Church, Dame Sarah has become the
OL,9,Fmost senior bishop and the spiritual
OL,10,Fleader of the Church and the worldwide
OL,11,FAnglican Communion.
OL,13,FCharles will be represented at the
OL,14,Fceremony by his son and heir William,
OL,15,Falongside his wife Catherine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
