PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FDame Sarah, who was named in the role
OL,8,Flast October, was congratulated at
OL,9,Fthat time by the King on assuming a
OL,10,Fposition "which is of such importance
OL,11,Fin the UK and across the global
OL,12,FAnglican Communion".
OL,14,FWhile she was confirmed in post at a
OL,15,FSt Paul's Cathedral ceremony in
OL,16,FJanuary, Wednesday will be the first
OL,17,Foccasion on which she delivers a
OL,18,Fsermon as Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,26,@rD@JOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
