CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FIn an interview with the BBC ahead of
OL,8,Fthe ceremony, she noted the
OL,9,F"significance of being the first
OL,10,Ffemale archbishop", and paid tribute
OL,11,Fto "the women that have supported me
OL,12,Fin my ministry, and also the men as
OL,13,Fwell".
OL,15,FShe previously pledged to speak out on
OL,16,Fmisogyny ` something she said she had
OL,17,Fexperienced herself and which she
OL,18,Finsisted must be spoken about "so that
OL,19,Fyou bring it out into the open".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@RO]sD@DOUuD@EO]zD@_OU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
