OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FDame Sarah has replaced Justin Welby
OL,8,Fin the role, after he announced his
OL,9,Fresignation in November 2024 over
OL,10,Ffailures in handling an abuse scandal.
OL,12,FShe has also previously acknowledged
OL,13,Fthe challenges ahead because of the
OL,14,F"legacy of deep harm and mistrust" she
OL,15,Fsaid existed after past safeguarding
OL,16,Ffailures in the Church.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FIn her first presidential address at
OL,8,Fthe Church's Synod ` also know as its
OL,9,Fparliament ` in February, Dame Sarah
OL,10,Fdescribed safeguarding as a
OL,11,F"fundamental, non-negotiable
OL,12,Fresponsibility, sharpened by our past
OL,13,Ffailings and shaped by the work we
OL,14,Fstill have to do".
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
