PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FIn her BBC interview this week, she
OL,8,Fsaid the Church was "seeking to become
OL,9,Fmore trauma informed, listening to
OL,10,Fsurvivors and victims of abuse", and
OL,11,Fshe added that "light should be shone
OL,12,Fon all our actions, and the more
OL,13,Fsenior we are, the more light should
OL,14,Fbe shone".
OL,16,FShe reaffirmed her "commitment to do
OL,17,Fall I can to ensure that the Church
OL,18,Fbecomes safer and also responds well
OL,19,Fto victims and survivors of abuse".
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@_O]sD@POUvD@IO]xD@TOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
