OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FWednesday's ceremony is scheduled to
OL,8,Fgo ahead without any specific safety
OL,9,Fmitigations being required amid the
OL,10,Fmeningitis outbreak in Kent.
OL,12,FDame Sarah, in a statement issued last
OL,13,Fweek, said her thoughts and prayers
OL,14,Fwere with the families of two young
OL,15,Fpeople who have died in the outbreak,
OL,16,Fsaying her "heart goes out to them in
OL,17,Ftheir devastating loss".
OL,26,@xD@LOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
