SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FThe service will not involve Holy
OL,8,FCommunion, but those gathered may
OL,9,Fexchange handshakes as is traditional
OL,10,Fin offering a sign of peace to those
OL,11,Fnearby.
OL,13,FOfficials have said they are keeping
OL,14,Fin contact with health authorities to
OL,15,Fmonitor the situation, but that the
OL,16,Fevent "remains categorised as low risk
OL,17,Fso will proceed as planned".
OL,26,@xD@GOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
