OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FWednesday's service will feature a
OL,8,Fmandate from the King ` as supreme
OL,9,Fgovernor of the Church of England `
OL,10,Fgiving instruction to install Dame
OL,11,FSarah.
OL,13,FIn nods to the diversity of the
OL,14,FAnglican Communion, various languages
OL,15,Fwill feature in the service, including
OL,16,Fsinging in Urdu, a Gospel reading in
OL,17,FSpanish and a prayer in the Bemba
OL,18,Flanguage of Zambia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
