PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer and
OL,8,FConservative Party leader Kemi
OL,9,FBadenoch are expected to be present,
OL,10,Fwith other faith leaders, charities,
OL,11,Fhealthcare workers and schoolchildren.
OL,13,FDame Sarah, who was chief nursing
OL,14,Fofficer in England before she was
OL,15,Fordained, has also invited NHS nurses
OL,16,Fand carers working in hospitals and
OL,17,Fhospices in Canterbury to attend the
OL,18,Fceremony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774433137
OL,3,CFirst woman to be enthroned as
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury in historic
OL,5,Cceremony
OL,7,FOther guests will include more than
OL,8,Ftwo dozen primates from the Anglican
OL,9,FCommunion ` Christian churches around
OL,10,Fthe world of which Dame Sarah is now
OL,11,Fthe spiritual leader.
OL,13,FAmong these will be some of the first
OL,14,Ffemale Anglican bishops from across
OL,15,FAfrica, who will join a procession
OL,16,Fthrough the cathedral.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
